# ORCA 6.0.1 - AIMD of Na+ solvated in 10 water molecules
# Method: r2SCAN-3c (fast composite DFT, good for water/ion interactions)
# MD: NVT Berendsen thermostat at 300 K, 0.5 fs timestep, 500 steps (250 fs)

! r2SCAN-3c TightSCF MD

%pal
  nprocs 1
end

%maxcore 7000

%md
  Timestep 0.5_fs
  Initvel 300_K
  Thermostat Berendsen 300_K Timecon 100.0_fs
  Dump Position Stride 5 Filename "trajectory.xyz"
  Run 500
end

